'''Beats of No Nation''' ni film yo muri Amerika yanditswe, itunganywa ,ifatwa amashusho , no iyoborwa na Cary Joji Fukunaga <ref>Beasts of No Nation - Rotten Tomatoes</ref>. Bikurikira umuhungu muto wabaye umusirikare mugihe igihugu cye cyari gifite intambara iteye ubwoba. Iyi filime yakorewe muri [[Gana]] ikinwamo na Idris Elba<ref>Idris Elba on 'Beasts of No Nation' and Making Grown Men Cry <nowiki>https://www.rollingstone.com</nowiki> › tv-news › idris-elba-on-...</ref>, Abraham Attah, Ama K. Abebrese, Grace Nortey, David Dontoh, na Opeyemi Fagbohungbe<ref>#47. "Beasts of No Nation" | | santamariatimes.com <nowiki>https://santamariatimes.com</nowiki> › 47-beasts-of-no-nation</ref>, iyi filime ishingiye ku gitabo cyo mu 2005 cyitwa izina rimwe na Uzodinma Iweala,  igitabo ubwacyo cyiswe izina. nyuma ya alubumu ya Fela Kuti <ref>(PDF) Fela Anikulapo-Kuti's "Beasts of No Nation": A Historical ... <nowiki>https://www.researchgate.net</nowiki> › ... › BEAST</ref>.

Yerekanwe mu gice cy’amarushanwa akomeye mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya 72 rya Venice<ref>'Beasts of No Nation': Venice Review - The Hollywood Reporter <nowiki>https://www.hollywoodreporter.com</nowiki> › general-news › b...</ref>,   aho yatsindiye igihembo cya Marcello Mastroianni<ref>BEASTS OF NO NATION - Levantine – Films <nowiki>https://www.levantine-films.com</nowiki> › Projects</ref> .  Iyi filime yerekanwe mu gice cyihariye cyo kwerekana iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime rya Toronto mu mwaka wa 2015,  ikanasohoka kuri Netflix ku isi yose ndetse no mu isohoka rito na Bleecker Street ku ya 16 Ukwakira 2015<ref>Beasts of No Nation: The most shocking Oscars snub? - CNN <nowiki>https://www.cnn.com</nowiki> › 2016/01/22 › africa › beasts-no-n...</ref>. 

=== Itangazamakuru ryo murugo ===
Filime yasohotse kuri Blu-ray na DVD na The Criterion Collection ku ya 31 Kanama 2021.<ref>Beasts of No Nation (2015) | The Criterion Collection <nowiki>https://www.criterion.com</nowiki> › films › 31756-beasts-of-no-n...</ref> 

=== Impaka ===
Mu mwaka wa 2015, Artnet yasohoye inyandiko ivuga ko Fukunaga yakoresheje ibikubiyemo atiriwe ashimira ibihangano by'umuhanzi wo muri Irlande<ref>Beasts of No Nation review: Netflix makes a visceral start in ... <nowiki>https://www.irishtimes.com</nowiki> › culture › film › beasts-of-no...</ref>, Richard Mosse,  umurimo we wari umaze kumenyekana cyane mu buhanzi kubera gukoresha firime ya infragre ndetse no kwerekana ishusho y'abasirikare b'abana muri Repubulika iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo<ref>Beasts of No Nation Is Uncompromisingly Brutal - Vulture <nowiki>https://www.vulture.com</nowiki> › 2015/10 › movie-review-beast...</ref>. Mu rwego rwo gushyigikira ikirego cyayo cyo gukopera, iyi ngingo yarimo kugereranya mu buryo butaziguye amakadiri ya buri muntu muri filime n'amafoto y'umwimerere ya Mosse.<ref>Did Film Director Rip Off Photographer Richard Mosse? <nowiki>https://news.artnet.com</nowiki> › art-world › did-beasts-no-nati...</ref>
